{"tid":962779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【退出中國市場？】三星天津工廠今關閉 2千多名員工仍待安置","createTime":"2018-12-31T06:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T17:32:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d9af7bfdd2264e6bf4cb1f12373eca56c82f16ec","tid":962779,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181231/large/1546233923_787c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F1546233923_787c.jpg&h=46089510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前有韓媒報道，三星電子決定於本月底停止天津手機工廠的生產運作，並已向員工公佈這決定。報道指三星電子之所以這樣決定，是因為三星手機在中國市場失利，以及三星將集中力量拓展印度及越南等新興市場。天津三星工廠於今日(31日)停工關閉，但工廠2千多名員工的安置問題，三星還未公佈具體方案。內媒記者到三星天津工廠，見部份員工正準備搬離宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n三星在華手機工廠分別設在天津和惠州，天津工廠主要負責智能手機出口。目前，三星正將其生產基地遷往勞動成本較低的越南和印度。<br />\n<br />\n手機工廠的關閉，與三星智能手機在中國的銷售表現不無關係。從市場份額佔比來看，2016年三星全年市場佔比為5.5%，2017年不到3%，2018年前三季度為0.9%。三星手機的節節敗退，一定程度上源於成本高企。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181231/59089228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59089228&d=Vzlor4zzsfsTuJsoLHP5MR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=b90b117d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59089228&h=b51b6d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181231/59089228</a>"},{"pid":"206162dec65c69b3cd46f40013e5ad2bf9d0b8cf","tid":962779,"uid":163826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"冇事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64be8eb3e58a27068868f2532980d52f915215a8","tid":962779,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"記得上年深圳廠已經執左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agr